   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Harmodios to Zenon [greeting. If you are in good health and everything else is to your] mind, it would be well. I myself am in good health. Antilochos(?), [who is handing you this letter is a relative of ours], and he has sailed up the river to your place [- - -]. You will do me a favour by receiving [him. Write to us if you have need of anything: we will do it] carefully. [Farewell. Year . .] Mesore 21.</ab>
         </div>
